WEBVTT


00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:02.420
the number one thing men crave from women

00:00:02.680 --> 00:00:04.840
men want to feel appreciated

00:00:04.841 --> 00:00:06.281
he's serving you

00:00:06.282 --> 00:00:10.021
whether that's driving you around so you can be the passenger princess

00:00:10.040 --> 00:00:11.820
or taking you out on dates

00:00:12.120 --> 00:00:14.400
simply being there to make you feel safe

00:00:14.401 --> 00:00:15.241
provided for

00:00:15.242 --> 00:00:16.361
and protected

00:00:16.362 --> 00:00:17.961
that's him serving you

00:00:17.962 --> 00:00:20.741
things he does for you is serving you

00:00:20.800 --> 00:00:25.660
the number one thing you can do to fuel his desire to continue to serve you

00:00:25.840 --> 00:00:27.736
is giving him gratitude.

00:00:27.737 --> 00:00:29.001
The  more appreciation,

00:00:29.002 --> 00:00:31.621
and gratitude you have for a man

00:00:31.760 --> 00:00:33.420
the more he wants to serve you,

00:00:33.440 --> 00:00:36.480
which in return serves them truly

00:00:36.481 --> 00:00:41.261
it's so simple to just acknowledge what they do for you and appreciate them!

00:00:41.280 --> 00:00:44.080
to say, “I acknowledge what you've done for us,

00:00:44.081 --> 00:00:45.521
thank you” yes,

00:00:45.522 --> 00:00:46.721
you're in this together

00:00:46.722 --> 00:00:51.781
but simply saying or giving appreciation really does go a long way for them

00:00:51.920 --> 00:00:55.200
you can say I know you've been at work all day and you're exhausted

00:00:55.201 --> 00:00:58.901
but I really appreciate what you're doing for us and our family

00:00:59.040 --> 00:01:00.840
Say I really appreciate it

00:01:00.841 --> 00:01:02.021
say thank you

00:01:02.400 --> 00:01:04.180
this will make the biggest difference

00:01:04.320 --> 00:01:06.300
to make someone feel seen

00:01:06.440 --> 00:01:10.500
Because we all have the desire to feel seen or heard for who we really are
